="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/adobe-podcasts-text-based-editing-turns-limitation-into-liberation-133001520.html">基于文本的编辑工具</a>进行。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>背景噪音通过一种名为“Enhance Speech”的人工智能工具进行处理，Adobe 宣称该工具可以将任何音频转换为“在专业录音室录制”的质量。 Adobe 声称它会自动消除背景噪音，同时为您提供混合滑块（如果您想保留任何背景噪音）。</p><p>这些新功能与跨<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/adobe-is-bringing-generative-ai-features-to-photoshop-after-effects-and-premiere-pro-130034491.html">Photoshop</a> 、Adobe Express 和 Illustrator <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/adobes-firefly-ai-is-now-commercially-available-on-photoshop-illustrator-and-express-130049419.html">的 Adob​​e Firefly for Enterprise Generative AI 商业版本</a>一起推出 - <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/adobe-is-bringing-generative-ai-features-to-photoshop-after-effects-and-premiere-pro-130034491.html">今年 3 月推出了测试版</a>。使用人工智能工具需要“生成积分”订阅计划，该计划应该“使客户能够将基于文本的提示转化为图像和矢量创作”。它还可以作为具有 Creative Cloud 付费计划的 Web 应用程序提供。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/adobe-premiere-pro-is-getting-an-ai-tool-to-cut-your-hems-and-haws-145019681.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/adobe-premiere-pro-is-getting-an-ai-tool-to-cut-your-hems-and-haws-145019681.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 01f7eb14-663c-48ff-8c24-2c851d74594c</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 13 Sep 2023 14:50:19 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694616620</ingested><modified> 2023-09-13T14:50:25+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content heigh